snippet: Iran's official news agency is reporting that three men convicted of killing an Iranian prosecutor in the country's restive border region with Pakistan have been executed....

headline.print_headline: 3 Men Convicted of Killing Iran Prosecutor Hanged
headline.main: 3 Men Convicted of Killing Iran Prosecutor Hanged

lead_paragraph: Iran's official news agency is reporting that three men convicted of killing an Iranian prosecutor in the country's restive border region with Pakistan have been executed.
